ket, sector, technology, top. This endpoint is available on all plans. This is not a search API but returns news by category.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"category\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"This parameter can be 1 of the following values <code>general, forex, crypto, merger</code>.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"general\",\n            \"forex\",\n            \"crypto\",\n            \"merger\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"minId\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Use this field to get only news after this ID. Default to 0\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"category\": \"general\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 921.42,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.935\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"financialmodelingprep.earnings_calendar.list.v1.6f2eca78\",\n      \"name\": \"List Earnings Calendar\",\n      \"description\": \"Stay informed on upcoming and past earnings announcements with the FMP Earnings Calendar API. Access key data, including announcement dates, estimated earnings per share (EPS), and actual EPS for publicly traded companies.\",\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"to\": \"2023-09-30\",\n          \"from\": \"2023-09-01\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"FMP offers a stock market data API covers real-time stock prices, historical prices and market news to stock fundamentals and company information. We provide one of the most accurate financial data available on the market. You can get historical prices, fundamental data, insider transactions, and much more that goes back 30 years in history.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 2.408,\n        \"success_rate\": 1\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"financialmodelingprep.search.exchange.variants.retrieve.v1.3e342578\",\n      \"name\": \"Search Exchange Variants\",\n      \"description\": \"Find where a given stock symbol is listed across multiple public exchanges.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Stock symbol\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"FMP offers a stock market data API covers real-time stock prices, historical prices and market news to stock fundamentals and company information. We provide one of the most accurate financial data available on the market. You can get historical prices, fundamental data, insider transactions, and much more that goes back 30 years in history.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 0,\n        \"success_rate\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"yahoo_finance.finance_search.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"Yahoo Finance Search\",\n      \"description\": \"Search for stocks, news, and companies using Yahoo Finance search API\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"q\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Search query (e.g., 'Apple', 'Tesla', 'technology stocks')\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"quotesCount\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Number of stock quotes to return (default: 10)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"newsCount\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Number of news articles to return (default: 5)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"listsCount\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Number of lists to return (default: 0)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"enableFuzzyQuery\",\n          \"type\": \"boolean\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Enable fuzzy search (default: true)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"enableCb\",\n          \"type\": \"boolean\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Enable company breakdown (default: false)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"enableNavLinks\",\n          \"type\": \"boolean\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Enable navigation links (default: false)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"enableResearchReports\",\n          \"type\": \"boolean\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Enable research reports (default: false)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"enableCulturalAssets\",\n          \"type\": \"boolean\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Enable cultural assets (default: false)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"recommendedCount\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Number of recommended results (default: 0)\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Yahoo Finance data provider using yfinance SDK for stock market data, news, and financial information\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 0,\n        \"success_rate\": 1\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"search_id\": \"b67e18b7-8684-4d79-ad0c-8008f2f42816\",\n  \"elapsed_time_ms\": 377.99\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durati